Package: fusionImage
Title: This package implemente three image fusion algorithms (High Pass
        Filter, Principal Component Analysis, and Gram-Schmidt), and
        ERGAS fussion quality index
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Paul", "Pesántez-Cobos", email = "paul_pz@hotmail.com", role = c("aut")),
