    person("Francisco", "Alonso-Sarría", email = "alonsarp@um.es", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Francisco Alonso-Sarria <alonsarp@um.es>
Description: This package implemente three image fussion algorithms (High Pass
    Filter, Principal Component Analysis, and Gram-Schmidt), and two fussion quality
    indices (ERGAS spatial and ERGAS spectral).
